txt.en: An empty basket can be found just outside Radagast's Cottage.\n\nYou should deposit the vegetables that you have collected into the empty basket.
'You have done much to aid my efforts.'
Radagast can be found in Rhosgobel.\n\nYou should talk to Radagast.
Radagast's garden can be found in Rhosgobel near Radagast's Cottage.\n\nYou should gather fruits and vegetables from Radagast's garden.
'There is much to do in the Vales, my friend.'
Put the vegetables in the empty basket outside of Radagast's cottage

'I do enjoy gardening now and again. It can be quite relaxing. However, I am so very busy that I have not had a single moment to tend to my vegetables and fruits. Would you be kind enough to pick the ripe plants and deposit them inside my cottage?'
There are many fruits and vegetables in Radagast's garden that are ripe for the picking.
'You have been most kind. I plan on using the vegetables to make a stew and the fruits for a pie. No, they are not for you nor I. These are to be a token of good will towards the Woodmen.'
